name: Tr3y Genesis Collection - El Pepe de James

metadata.name: El Pepe de James #1/5
metadata.description:
James had always been fascinated by frogs. He loved the way they hopped around, their slimy skin, and the way they caught flies with their long, sticky tongues. So, when he stumbled upon a strange vial filled with a glowing green liquid while rummaging through his grandpa's old shed, he couldn't resist the temptation to try it out.

Without a second thought, James uncorked the vial and chugged its contents in one go. Immediately, he felt a tingling sensation coursing through his veins and his vision began to blur. He stumbled backwards, trying to keep his balance, but it was no use. With a loud thud, James hit the ground and blacked out.

When he awoke, James was shocked to find that he had been transformed into a half-frog hybrid.
